data.description: Buyer financing fell through, back on the market with a price improvement! Lender cancelled on the day before closing, all inspections and repairs are completed. Electric box and roof both updated for sale! Beautiful updated 4-bedroom 1 bathroom home located in the heart of Plant City. AC system, electrical and plumbing updated in 2019, and the roof was re-rolled in 2023. When you step into this home you are greeted with a beautifully upgraded kitchen which has granite counter tops and a custom mosaic back splash, open to the dining area which is perfect for entertaining. This home features a split floor plan with 3 bedrooms on end of the home and 1 on the other. The spacious living room is versatile and has endless potential. Beautiful ceramic tile and laminate flooring throughout the common areas. Outside there is large backyard with a 92in fence giving privacy. New landscaping has been completed in the front of the home. Conveniently located minutes from I-4 and close to everything the area has to offer. If you are looking for a quiet, friendly neighborhood this home is for you!
